    "name": "Manga Ninja 漫画忍者",
    "steam_appid": 3061370,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《漫画忍者》是一款创新的平台跳跃游戏。在这个独特的漫画世界里，你将扮演忍者，踏上充满挑战的冒险之旅。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061370/extras/17831f7ed3b53d48592b22de26810a27.webp?t=1762397239\" width=760 height=39 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >基础玩法</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与传统的跳跃游戏不同，你无法直接跳跃，而是需要巧妙地运用忍者技能。通过发射手里剑，你可以在空中制造抓钩，然后快速将抓钩发射到手里剑的位置，实现惊险刺激的位移。这种独特的移动方式将为你带来前所未有的游戏体验。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>投掷飞镖</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061370/extras/c92c9eadbd7e2cebc7d3f6f520e0a417.poster.avif?t=1762397239\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061370/extras/c92c9eadbd7e2cebc7d3f6f520e0a417.webm?t=1762397239\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061370/extras/c92c9eadbd7e2cebc7d3f6f520e0a417.mp4?t=1762397239\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>发射抓钩</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061370/extras/d9b7530a48124eb84d8c439d7f78565f.poster.avif?t=1762397239\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061370/extras/d9b7530a48124eb84d8c439d7f78565f.webm?t=1762397239\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061370/extras/d9b7530a48124eb84d8c439d7f78565f.mp4?t=1762397239\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多种功能的飞镖</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061370/extras/84c9cdf864f5fc8c5e28f3a9e1690758.poster.avif?t=1762397239\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061370/extras/84c9cdf864f5fc8c5e28f3a9e1690758.webm?t=1762397239\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061370/extras/17831f7ed3b53d48592b22de26810a27.webp?t=1762397239\" width=760 height=39 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >丰富的场景</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将在充满日式特色的各种场景中展开冒险：古老的道场、静谧的竹林、风景如画的运河，以及宏伟的日式城堡。每个场景都经过精心设计，拥有独特的视觉风格，充满挑战和乐趣。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >道场</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061370/extras/97f59c1dc7b3ecb140affb5b9f3bc530.poster.avif?t=1762397239\" width=426 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061370/extras/97f59c1dc7b3ecb140affb5b9f3bc530.webm?t=1762397239\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061370/extras/97f59c1dc7b3ecb140affb5b9f3bc530.mp4?t=1762397239\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >竹林</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061370/extras/1436db5a47379cc828d6427bdbc2d564.avif?t=1762397239\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061370/extras_big/1436db5a47379cc828d6427bdbc2d564.avif?t=1762397239 width=1560 height=920 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >运河</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061370/extras/7b7ebee97e6e6e1b9d45532325797ed8.avif?t=1762397239\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061370/extras_big/7b7ebee97e6e6e1b9d45532325797ed8.avif?t=1762397239 width=1560 height=848 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >洞穴</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061370/extras/e3b520e1db79a426ec2ff66d494744ce.avif?t=1762397239\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061370/extras_big/e3b520e1db79a426ec2ff66d494744ce.avif?t=1762397239 width=1560 height=938 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >城堡屋顶</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061370/extras/164172a36b00022d573202b56c31663a.avif?t=1762397239\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061370/extras_big/164172a36b00022d573202b56c31663a.avif?t=1762397239 width=1560 height=856 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >城堡内部</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061370/extras/cc6f1a32ab186a37a68073f361c071b2.avif?t=1762397239\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061370/extras_big/cc6f1a32ab186a37a68073f361c071b2.avif?t=1762397239 width=1560 height=938 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >灯笼节</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061370/extras/2f759dc4546905e7bfbd5908d33bb0ff.avif?t=1762397239\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061370/extras_big/2f759dc4546905e7bfbd5908d33bb0ff.avif?t=1762397239 width=1560 height=1018 /></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一个具有日式风格的场景都被装进了漫画格子里，并且为不同场景配置了不同的陷阱和挑战。玩家在不同场景中节奏是不一样的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061370/extras/17831f7ed3b53d48592b22de26810a27.webp?t=1762397239\" width=760 height=39 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于开发者</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是我开发的第一款游戏作品，把本科时的游戏打磨上架。踏上取经路比到达灵山更重要。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最开始他是这样的，但是再给周围的朋友试玩的时候，大家的反馈非常好，让我有了继续开发下去的动力<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061370/extras/746ac0e33026a24572fde40330501ef6.avif?t=1762397239\" width=1462 height=823 /></span>我参考了日本传统文化和漫画的美术风格，游戏设计上也遵循着日式极简的风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏的挑战是直观的，但是玩家会在一次次挑战中上头，在通过一个个漫画格子里找到成就感。希望大家玩的开心</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎大家关注我的b站:玄清侠Congee</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >qq群:1023172157</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
